---
layout: section.liquid
title: Books
permalink: /notes/books/
description: Notes on books I've read
---
<p>
  I take a lot of notes about the books I read and I find myself often in a place where I'd like to share a particular
  passage from a book, hence this section.
</p>

<div class="books-grid">
  {% assign category = collections.notesByCategory["books"] %}
  {% for item in category.notes %}
    <a href="{{ item.postUrl }}">
      <article class="book-card">
        <div class="book-card-cover">
          <img
            src="/assets/notes/reading/{{ item.postUrl | split: '/' | last }}.jpg"
            alt="Cover of {{ item.title }}"
            loading="lazy"
          >
        </div>
        <footer class="book-card-info">
          <h3>{{ item.title }}</h3>
          {% if item.author %}
            <p class="book-card-author">{{ item.author }}</p>
          {% endif %}
        </footer>
      </article>
    </a>
  {% endfor %}
</div>
